oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Plantation Party excerpts - Duke Of Paducah comedy routines
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three home-recorded excerpts from NBC's Plantation Party, featuring comedy routines by the Duke Of Paducah. Various dates, including circa late-November/early-December 1942 ('Thanksgiving' routine).
